Ministerial order
NÂ° 004/2016 OF 08/01/2016 DETERMINING RULES GOVERVERNING CODE OF CONDUCT OF HEADMASTERS, TEACHERS AND STUDENTS
The Minister of Education; Pursuant to the Constitution of the Republic of Rwanda of 2003 as revised in 2015, especially in Articles 121, 122 and 176; Pursuant to Law no23/2012 of 15/06/2012 governing the organization and functioning of Nursery, Primary and Secondary Education, especially in Articles24 and 27; After consideration and approval by Cabinet, in its session of 14/05/2015; HEREBY ORDERS: